metadata.name: Skywalker #01
metadata.description:
The Skywalkers are a collection of unique 1/1 NFT photographs created by itsdavey.

Over the last decade I've traveled all over the world in search of that perfect highline. This collection will take you on that journey along side me.

A highline is a 1 inch wide piece of webbing. After applying tension, highliners walk across the line using balance and focus. Don't worry, walkers are often safely attached to the line, in the event of a misstep the rope arrests the walkers fall.
